	<div id="section3" class="container-fluid">
		<h1>Quotes</h1>
		<p>Linus Torvalds drive and ambition to create Linux came from his fiery distaste of Microsoft, so naturally a lot of his quotes are directed towards the inferior state of Microsoft.</p>
		<div class="quotes">
			<p>"Really, I'm not out to destroy Microsoft. That will just be a completely unintentional side effect."</p>
			<p>"Microsoft isn't evil, they just make really crappy operating systems."</p>
			<p>"Don't you think that if Microsoft actually had some really foolproof patent, they'd just tell us and go, "nyaah, nyaah, nyaah!"?</p>
			<p>"If Microsoft ever does applications for Linux it means I've won.</p>
		</div>
